reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great Bag, and Big
reviews.reviewText: I love this bag, at first I was not sure how I was going to feel about it, because I thought it might be manly looking at pictures. once I got it and switched all of my things into it, I was pleased with how it looked. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I love this bag
reviews.reviewText: It came the exact same day I ordered it and not late at night either but early in the afternoon. It was exactly as described. It's made a very good quality I can't tell if it's real leather or not but I guess that's a good thing. It has exact right amount of pockets and little cubbies and apartments not so many that you can't keep track of stuff and it takes forever to find anything but just the right amount. There's a space for just about everything or anything you might want to carry with you. Perfect for laptops and notebooks and school and work. It comes with two extra leather tabs for the zippers in case one gets damaged or ripped. The only complaint I have is that the shoulder strap does not come off it's permanently fixed to the bag but other than that it's absolutely perfect. It's waterproof just as it says I spilled water on it and it just beads up and rolls right off. The flat part that goes over the top has two zipper compartments on the outside and then two plastic clips to hold it down with a leather handle on top then on the back side there's a zipper compartment. It has one open pocket on each end when you flip up the top there's one main compartment that has two slots one for your laptop and that compartment has a strap that goes over the top and velcro's to hold your laptop in place. Then a compartment in front of that which has the main area and then to pockets. Then there's an outer zipper compartment that has holders for pins or pencils and pockets for other things and eight little pockets for business cards or credit cards something like that and that's about it. Like I said not too many compartments but just the right amount.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 21, 2023
reviews.reviewText: The bag isn’t bad, per se, but I did find it not as structurally strong as I expected. It sagged once I added my usual work items to it, which made it feel awkward and unwieldy. I thought it would keep its shape more. It was also a lot larger than I expected, which isn’t necessarily bad, but I’m a fairly small guy, so it made it seem huge in comparison to my previous bag. The fabric is nice, though, and the quality is good. I ended up switching back to my old bag for work, though. I use this for traveling only.
It met my expectations and for a very reasonable price.

Muy buen producto, compre el XL y tiene muy buen tamaño y buena capacidad. Es un poco incomodo lo del velcro, ya que si levantas la mochila de la asa es muy probable que se abra, pero sirve completamente para su función
Nice quality, beautiful style, great price
